Package: whoregionalmap
Version: 1.0.0
Title: Cloropleth WHO Regional maps using shapes from WHO
Authors@R: person("Takuya", "Yamanaka", email = "yamanakat@who.int", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Loads WHO shape files (2022) and provides a wrapper to ggplot2. 
  Adapted from scripts from Phillipe Glaziou.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0),
  ggplot2 (>= 3.3.0),
  scales (>= 1.1.0)
